CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Junee Limited and its wholly-owned subsidiary, OPS Interior Design Consultant Limited ('OPS HK'), provides quality interior design, fit-out and maintenance services to both residential and commercial clients in the Hong Kong interior design market. The interior design service involves preliminary consulting services, conceptualizing clients' design ideas with layout plans, and producing detailed design drawings. Fit-out work generally includes any activities making an interior space suitable for residential or commercial purposes.
